{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01C1BNbmgJWYJT5db7RnUi2E","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (JSF + JPA + EJB + CDI on Open Liberty) → Spring Boot 3.2.5 (REST + Spring Data JPA + embedded Tomcat)\n\n**Overall Outcome:** Success - Application builds, runs, and passes all 10 smoke tests.\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n- JSF frontend → REST API (the original app used JSF/XHTML pages for CRUD; migrated to a RESTful JSON API preserving all CRUD operations)\n- EJB `@Stateless` facade → Spring `@Service` + `@Repository` (Spring Data JPA)\n- Open Liberty server → Embedded Tomcat via Spring Boot\n- WAR packaging → Executable JAR\n- `persistence.xml` + `server.xml` → `application.properties`\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE deps with Spring Boot starters, changed parent POM\n- Dockerfile: Added Maven build step, changed CMD to run Spring Boot JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/AddressBookApplication.java: Spring Boot entry point\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/entity/Contact.java: JPA entity (migrated)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/repository/ContactRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repo\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/service/ContactService.java: Service layer\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/controller/ContactController.java: REST controller\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config\n- smoke.py: 10 smoke tests for all CRUD operations\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/ (entire old source tree - 6 Java files)\n- src/main/webapp/ (JSF XHTML pages, web.xml, faces-config.xml, CSS)\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n- src/main/resources/Bundle.properties\n- src/main/resources/ValidationMessages.properties\n```\n\n### Test Results\n- **10/10 smoke tests passed**\n- Tests cover: empty list, create, get, update, list non-empty, count, second create, pagination, delete, 404 handling\n\n### Error Handling\n- **No errors encountered** during the migration\n- **Warning (non-blocking):** Hibernate logged `HHH90000025: H2Dialect does not need to be specified explicitly` - this is informational only and does not affect functionality"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":484,"cache_read_input_tokens":61667,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":484,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":636},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05fe22a4-ca64-46f0-a504-1ec9b1d1a23f","uuid":"ff1a70a8-2bb2-4317-9b5a-a41021234ada"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":625015,"duration_api_ms":622729,"num_turns":56,"result":"---\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (JSF + JPA + EJB + CDI on Open Liberty) → Spring Boot 3.2.5 (REST + Spring Data JPA + embedded Tomcat)\n\n**Overall Outcome:** Success - Application builds, runs, and passes all 10 smoke tests.\n\n### Key Migration Decisions\n- JSF frontend → REST API (the original app used JSF/XHTML pages for CRUD; migrated to a RESTful JSON API preserving all CRUD operations)\n- EJB `@Stateless` facade → Spring `@Service` + `@Repository` (Spring Data JPA)\n- Open Liberty server → Embedded Tomcat via Spring Boot\n- WAR packaging → Executable JAR\n- `persistence.xml` + `server.xml` → `application.properties`\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Replaced Jakarta EE deps with Spring Boot starters, changed parent POM\n- Dockerfile: Added Maven build step, changed CMD to run Spring Boot JAR\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/AddressBookApplication.java: Spring Boot entry point\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/entity/Contact.java: JPA entity (migrated)\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/repository/ContactRepository.java: Spring Data JPA repo\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/service/ContactService.java: Service layer\n- src/main/java/com/example/addressbook/controller/ContactController.java: REST controller\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config\n- smoke.py: 10 smoke tests for all CRUD operations\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/ (entire old source tree - 6 Java files)\n- src/main/webapp/ (JSF XHTML pages, web.xml, faces-config.xml, CSS)\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n- src/main/resources/Bundle.properties\n- src/main/resources/ValidationMessages.properties\n```\n\n### Test Results\n- **10/10 smoke tests passed**\n- Tests cover: empty list, create, get, update, list non-empty, count, second create, pagination, delete, 404 handling\n\n### Error Handling\n- **No errors encountered** during the migration\n- **Warning (non-blocking):** Hibernate logged `HHH90000025: H2Dialect does not need to be specified explicitly` - this is informational only and does not affect functionality","session_id":"05fe22a4-ca64-46f0-a504-1ec9b1d1a23f","total_cost_usd":5.236168780000004,"usage":{"input_tokens":42,"cache_creation_input_tokens":49708,"cache_read_input_tokens":1792507,"output_tokens":20084,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":49708}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":69376,"outputTokens":4504,"cacheReadInputTokens":151756,"cacheCreationInputTokens":18851,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.10450828000000001,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":515,"outputTokens":160,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.003945000000000001,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":42,"outputTokens":20084,"cacheReadInputTokens":1792507,"cacheCreationInputTokens":49708,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":5.127715500000002,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"14cd2bf6-cbcc-409c-be8b-ce4f7692b642"}
